			<div class="page-content">

	<h1 class="title h0">新規アカウントを作成する</h1>

  	※お名前に旧字体が含まれるお客様は新字体でご入力ください（邉・邊・髙など）
	<form method="post" action="/account" id="create_customer" accept-charset="UTF-8" data-login-with-shop-sign-up="true"><input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="create_customer" /><input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓" />

		<div class="krown-columns-container one-whole">

			


      <div class="krown-column-container one-half first">
				<label for="last_name" class="hidden">姓</label>
				<input type="text" value="" name="customer[last_name]" id="last_name" placeholder="姓"  autocapitalize="words" required>
			</div>

      <div class="krown-column-container one-half last">
				<label for="first_name" class="hidden">名</label>
				<input type="text" value="" name="customer[first_name]" id="first_name" placeholder="名"  autocapitalize="words" autofocus required>
			</div>

      <div class="krown-column-container one-whole first last">
				<label for="email" class="hidden">メールアドレス</label>
				<input type="email" value="" name="customer[email]" id="email" placeholder="メールアドレス"  autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" required>
			</div>

      <div class="krown-column-container one-whole first last">
				<label for="password" class="hidden">パスワード</label>
				<input type="password" value="" name="customer[password]" id="create_password" placeholder="パスワード"  required>
			</div>

			<div class="login-actions">
				<input class="button button--solid button--wide" type="submit" value="作成">
			</div>
          <div class="krown-column-container one-whole first last rte">
            <p>「作成」を押した時点で、<a href="/policies/terms-of-service" target="_blank">利用規約</a>及び<a href="/policies/privacy-policy" target="_blank">プライバシーポリシー</a>に同意したとみなします。</p>
          </div>
		</div>

	</form>

</div>


